Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:34.62,italics top arial 20,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once, the residents of the demon \Nrealm marched across the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:37.82,Episode Title,Episode title sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Episode 2  Attack of the Xuán Guǐ Zōng!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:38.00,italics top arial 20,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,seeking to scorch human the realm. \NThis was the War of Fading Dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.29,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity, at the brink of extinction,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:45.98,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,sought the guidance of the \NXian immortals to give birth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:48.14,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,to countless weapons for \Ntheir final counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.32,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,These are the Shén Huì Mó Xiè.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.72,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary treasures of supernatural \Nstrength forged to let man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:56.93,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,stand on even footing against demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.00,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,With their incredible power,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:03.10,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,the demons were forced back to \Nthe depths of their own realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:06.64,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,and peace returned to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:11.21,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,The few intact Shén Huì Mó Xiè
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:15.20,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,that had survived the war \Nwere enshrined on holy ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:20.13,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,to ensure their incredible power would \Nnot fall into hands of the wicked,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:24.61,italics arial 20,Narration,0000,0000,0000,,and watched over by the Hù Yìn Shī.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:32.28,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,My clan, the Dān, are responsible for the \NDuàn Jiàn Cí shrine where one is enshrined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:34.57,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,It is the sword named Tiān Xing Jiàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.57,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,And even among the many Shén Huì Mó Xiè,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:41.68,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,it is said to have extraordinarily \Ndangerous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:46.82,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,But a group calling themselves \Nthe Xuán Guǐ Zōng attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:49.08,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,hoping to pillage the mystic blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:54.26,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I see...  I have heard \Nthat Miè Tiān Hái,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:56.92,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,who leads the Xuán Guǐ Zōng,\Nis consumed by an unearthly fixation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.26,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,on valuable and treasured swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:03.42,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,But to think he'd be so brazen as to set his \Nsights on a legendary Shén Huì Xiè Mó?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:04.59,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness gracious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:09.18,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not saying so \Nearlier, but my name is Dān Fěi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:14.08,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Though I lack in strength, I am one of the \NHù Yìn Shī who guard the Duàn Jiàn Cí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.87,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.97,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I am... just call me Guǐ Niǎo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:25.88,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a simple wanderer,\Ntoo insignificant to be called by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:31.15,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,You were actually saved by \Nthis fellow, Shāng Bù Huàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.76,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.77,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,I was just caught up in your mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.91,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Still, after raiding its hiding place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.81,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,the Xuán Guǐ Zōng should \Nhave what they were after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:46.21,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Why chase you all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:51.94,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,No... the Tiān Xing Jiàn is still secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:55.97,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,The pedestal it sits upon \Nhas a seal placed upon it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.87,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,so that it can not be taken from the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.98,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Then the key to this seal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.65,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,The sword's handle and guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:12.67,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,The Tiān Xing Jiàn's blade stands alone, \Nsealed within the Duàn Jiàn Cí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:18.78,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Affixing its handle and guard and \Nrestoring it to its original form
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:23.00,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,is the only way to remove \Nit from its pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.27,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Might I see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:28.24,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.46,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Since my predecessor passed the \Nduty of a Hù Yìn Shī onto me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:42.66,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I have carried it with me at all times, \Nvaluing it more than my life as I protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:47.21,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,My older brother was entrusted with \Nthe handle in the same fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:52.96,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,But my brother... was killed \Nwhen Miè Tiān Hái arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.36,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, Lady Dān Fěi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.08,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.35,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Avenge my brother, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.20,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I will strike down Miè Tiān Hái.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.84,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to retrieve the Tiān \NXing Jiàn's handle as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:13.54,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to tell me your big brother \Nwas weaker than his sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.06,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.97,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,My brother was a first-rate swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.82,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I pale in comparison to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:24.20,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,So how exactly are you gonna kill the man
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:27.33,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,who killed your brother,\Nif you're not even as good as him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:30.36,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,You might want to cool your \Nhead and think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.85,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:37.37,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,But still, the Shén Huì Mó Xiè have \Nbeen targeted by foul villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:42.57,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I know there are those who will \Ncome to my aid, if called upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:49.12,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,But of course! And I, Guǐ Niǎo, \Nwill gladly accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:52.22,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:54.93,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,To ignore the call to duty \Nis to show cowardice,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:59.53,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't you say, most honorable hero,\NShāng Bù Huàn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:03.15,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny. I flat-out refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:06.51,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:10.00,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,The ancient Shén Huì Mó \NXiè and their fearsome power
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:13.12,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,are on the verge into falling \Ninto villainous hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.24,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,None of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:18.84,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a hero, a saint, or your servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.88,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,And I make a point to avoid annoying trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:26.82,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,But you saved me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.76,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,That was... the spur of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.04,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,And a bit of goading, from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:35.59,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I didn't do \Nit because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:38.63,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Still playing the selfish oaf...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.61,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me make it clear, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:47.64,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of getting involved any\Nfurther with a shrewd bastard like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.62,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling yourself Guǐ Niǎo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:55.34,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe now you can risk your own \Nneck playing good Samaritan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.49,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.56,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,He's so upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.47,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.54,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:10.67,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,He's bound to be in a better \Nmood when you next see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.86,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.56,main arial 20,Nerd,0000,0000,0000,,You called, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:25.04,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,What has become of the Hù Yìn Shī girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.31,main arial 20,Nerd,0000,0000,0000,,We've no new information, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:31.01,main arial 20,Nerd,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to find the whereabouts \Nof this Shāng Bù Huàn
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.42,main arial 20,Nerd,0000,0000,0000,,who Cán Xiōng informed us of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:37.08,main arial 20,Liè Mèi,0000,0000,0000,,Our men are stationed \Nalong nearly every road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.66,main arial 20,Liè Mèi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple matter of \Ntime until he is found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.54,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago I started my \Ncollection priceless, mystic blades
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.51,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,whose names echo across the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:57.44,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,but there are none that compare to \Na work like the Tiān Xing Jiàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:02.09,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,It is the very incarnation \Nof immortal secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:09.11,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,The notion of leaving it in a dusty Hù \NYìn Shī shack is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:13.25,main arial 20,Liè Mèi,0000,0000,0000,,You are a sword saint unrivaled \Nthroughout the land, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:18.19,main arial 20,Liè Mèi,0000,0000,0000,,Only an incomparable masterpiece \Nis fit to hang at your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.75,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me the flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:25.10,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,I desire only the key to unlock \Nthe seal of the Duàn Jiàn Cí...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.45,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,The sword guard the girl has.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.47,main arial 20,MTH,0000,0000,0000,,Obtain it as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:35.76,main arial 20,Nerd,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. It will be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.96,italics arial 20,Liè Mèi,0000,0000,0000,,If I obtain the Tiān Xing Jiàn's guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:45.06,italics arial 20,Liè Mèi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much favor Lord \NTiān Hái will show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.80,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,This should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.30,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.89,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,I've written letters calling \Nupon important allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.71,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,since we will be challenging Miè Tiān Hái.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.20,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,You have power over birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.37,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,It will deliver the letters \Nto the nearest town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:25.73,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,And the bird master there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:31.42,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,will then send them to their destinations, \Nalong with different birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.73,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Are you always so well-prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:38.09,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Dealing with people is a like \Nslipping through a hole in net.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:44.42,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing the best methods for that \Nsort of thing is almost my only strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:50.05,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,But Sir Guǐ Niǎo, why go so far to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:55.45,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Due to certain circumstances, I am \Nacquainted with Miè Tiān Hái.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:56.72,main arial 20,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.04,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,You know him yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:04.02,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... and the Bones of Creation\Nis a dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:12.24,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,With the great power of the Shén Huì Mó Xiè,\Nhe would surely bring ruin to the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:18.72,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you appeal to Sir Shāng with \Nsuch a reasonable argument before he left?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.31,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he might have agreed then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:28.72,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he won't need convincing \Nto come to our aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:34.01,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,But before, he said he \Nwouldn't help us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:40.56,main arial 20,XY,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we travel down different roads \Nright now, our destination is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:45.52,main arial 20,DF,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very mysterious \Nperson, Sir Guǐ Niǎo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:11:02.31,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief! Maybe now I can sleep on \Nsomething soft, with a roof over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.48,main arial 20,Villagers,0000,0000,0000,,Right and—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:11.46,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:20.51,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let me have one of your shaobing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:25.21,main arial 20,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,I'm closed for business \Ntoday! Try somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.88,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere else...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:38.99,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I just want to buy some food.\NI've even got money to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:42.03,main arial 20,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,You can take whatever you want, but please,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.21,main arial 20,Shop,0000,0000,0000,,get out of here right now! \NBefore it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:47.80,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:59.52,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's wrong with this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.68,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.22,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,"Any who trade with this man or speak to him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:15.82,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,will be marked as a sworn enemy \Nof the Xuán Guǐ Zōng."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.69,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'm not sleeping indoors tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:23.93,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least I got something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.88,main arial 20,Shòu Yún Xiāo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Shāng Bù Huàn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.53,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:43.72,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,If I was him, I probably wouldn't want \Nto give my name to some damn stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:51.72,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,You make this Shāng fellow \Nsound like quite an eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:56.20,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy's been through Hell, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.34,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's being real cautious about anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:03.57,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,in this country who's on the side of the\Nroad and making strange assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:09.94,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't Shāng Bù Huàn,\Nyou can ignore this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:16.68,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,But the Xuán Guǐ Zōng are waiting \Nin ambush in the wilderness ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:22.41,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like this Shāng \Nguy's got really awful luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:42.81,main arial 20,Liè Mèi,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found you, Shāng Bù Huàn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.71,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the ones who posted \Nthose weird warnings in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.25,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:50.22,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.42,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Did you like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.09,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Can't say it's much of a likeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:14:00.89,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Might ask you to redraw it with \Nme looking a bit more handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.05,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.97,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure the picture on \Nyour memorial is much nicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:19.84,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I cut ties \Nto the Hù Yìn Shī girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:24.07,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask about where they are,\Nbut I've got no answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.95,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:29.95,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that saves the trouble \Nof questioning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:34.72,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to \Navenge Cán Xiōng, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.02,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it's gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:46.94,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, was this Cán Xiōng \Nyour relative or your lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.05,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:52.95,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,That fool is just the Xuán \NGuǐ Zōng's disgrace,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.26,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,who was beaten by some unknown vagrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:15:01.05,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,If he were reborn, I'd return \Nhim to the underworld myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.69,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,You want to avenge someone \Nyou barely care about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.94,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:09.42,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,This is simply about saving face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:12.69,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,The Xuán Guǐ Zōng's soldiers \Ncan not accept defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:17.97,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,If someone has defied us \Nand managed to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.13,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:24.07,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the policy of\Nyour leader, Miè Tiān Hái?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.95,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.71,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,The Master is a very proud man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:33.83,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,I could understand if he was risking \Nhis own life for his pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:39.75,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,But sending your servants to die \Nin vain isn't exactly praiseworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:47.28,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,You're still confused about who'll \Ndie and who'll do the killing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.70,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,How deliciously optimistic of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.64,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:01.96,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Not knowing how a fight to the death will\Nend is why people draw their swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:07.11,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,I'd explain that to you, \Nbut I doubt you'd listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:10.23,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Let me correct you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:13.89,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,You deserve death, and will die,\NShāng Bù Huàn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:16.66,main arial 20,Juǎn Cán Yún,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.10,main arial 20,Juǎn Cán Yún,0000,0000,0000,,Let those within earshot hear my words!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.13,main arial 20,Juǎn Cán Yún,0000,0000,0000,,Let those who can see bear witness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.86,main arial 20,Juǎn Cán Yún,0000,0000,0000,,Arriving like a storm, shaking the earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.44,main arial 20,Juǎn Cán Yún,0000,0000,0000,,The warrior whose name is \Nknown throughout the East!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:39.98,main arial 20,Juǎn Cán Yún,0000,0000,0000,,I am called the Frozen Wonder!\NJuǎn Cán Yún and his spear have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.61,main arial 20,Juǎn Cán Yún,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Aren't we fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:49.02,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah... What are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:53.29,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! That's kind of a rude \Nway to react to your savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:56.43,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you spare some gratitude \Nor astonishment or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.33,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's pretty obvious, but we're \Nin the middle of something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:01.30,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna get hurt, back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:08.96,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm here to take the fight \Nthat's been picked with you off your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.94,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,What idiocy is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.91,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:17.34,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I just told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.55,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,I'm known as the Frozen Wonder, Juǎn Cán Yún!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:24.31,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,You've probably heard of me, right? \NI'm kind of a big deal lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.58,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,I get it... you're one of those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.87,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,who goes around thinking \Nwhatever's convenient to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:30.92,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever listened to\Nsomeone in your entire life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.74,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you! I came here to save you,\Nso what's with the attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:40.32,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you trying to save me, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.73,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Why? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.21,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why are the Xuán Guǐ Zōng\Nafter you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.23,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:51.88,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Get both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:55.35,main arial 20,Goon,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them, including the young one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:59.13,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the circumstances,\Nthe fool's standing against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:02.26,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,If he wants to die that badly,\Nlet's grant his wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.16,main arial 20,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.50,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,What the—?! Where was that fired from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.47,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,As there are those who see \Nnothing with both eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.55,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,there are those who can see \Nvast distances with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:27.07,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,My gaze is the path of an arrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.82,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,piercing those who fail to turn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:36.92,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,When fighting someone in earnest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.83,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,There's but one thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:42.20,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,Telling them you're going \Nto kill them is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.43,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much, Juǎn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:02.27,main arial 20,Goon,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Liè Mèi, that came from \Nthe other side of those woods!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:06.59,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That can't be! No one could land \Nan arrow from that distance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.90,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man, there he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:16.23,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm not getting any action, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.16,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:22.82,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,I'd stay put if I were you, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:27.09,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Move around too much, and you'll \Nget in the big man's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.31,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,It's a messed-up thing\Nmy bro Shòu tends to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.65,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,He hates to stand out too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.72,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,but he's an expert at stealing the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:39.85,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Your bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.88,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't met him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:46.69,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,But he said he was going on \Nbefore me to get a look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.55,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the one-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:52.23,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,He had an odd bow, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.24,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.42,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,You saw my bro's one eye and steel bow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:20:00.27,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,and didn't recognize him as the \NSharp-Eyed Impaler, Shòu Yún Xiāo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.67,main arial 20,CY,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live underwater or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.38,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! And leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.75,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.07,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor walking, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:36.37,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were just weaklings, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:38.61,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,Quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:46.45,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,You! Are you the Sharp-Eyed Impaler?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.52,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,None other!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:55.57,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,To see my arrows loosed and \Nface me without running...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:21:01.23,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, you Xuán Guǐ Zōng\Ndogs are impressively bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.62,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Such nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.52,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how skilled you are with that bow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.14,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,how can you fight us at this range?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:29.28,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Even with your speed,\Nyou'll only be able to hit two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:33.96,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the blade of the one left \Nstanding will send your head flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.42,0:21:39.17,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Your famous name, known through the land,\Ncomes to its end here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.40,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Sharp-Eyed Impaler!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:45.24,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now... we'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:54.51,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! Have you gone mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:09.94,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,If you think people can \Nchoose how they die...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:13.56,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,You're gravely mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:19.44,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,You dogs don't realize that your place\Nof dying has been chosen for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.74,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:31.98,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:38.59,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.52,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,For you to fall over from that blow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:52.77,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I overestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:57.63,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,I imagined you would've steadied \Nyour footing with one less step.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:02.60,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.33,0:23:09.29,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,Not many get a chance to choose \Nwhere they will die, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:16.84,main arial 20,LM,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this! I will repay this dishonor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.37,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:29.84,main arial 20,SY,0000,0000,0000,,I ask you again: are you Shāng Bù Huàn?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:31.94,main arial 20,BH,0000,0000,0000,,And what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:49.93,Next Episode Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time  "The Woman In Night Devil Forest"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:42.95,italics arial 20,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A voice whispers in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:45.08,italics arial 20,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A suspicious, enticing lullaby...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:47.57,italics arial 20,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A woman's devilishness is \Nin full bloom at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:49.93,italics arial 20,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fall for the deception, and lose your life.
